  "title": "Front Office - Guest Services Agent",
  "description": "<p>The Guest Services Agent is responsible for creating unique, memorable and personal experiences for our guests during the process of check-in, check-out, reservations and rooms enquiries, must have an intuitive responsiveness to the expressed and unexpressed wishes and needs of our guests.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Core Responsibilities</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide excellent service, build strong relationships, anticipate and exceed the guests’ needs</li>\n  <li>Take ownership of guests issues or problems and take action to resolve problems immediately</li>\n  <li>Recognise and resolve problems by seeking, examining, and interpreting information from different sources to determine cause and develop solutions</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The Ideal Candidate:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Good command of English in both verbal and written communication</li>\n  <li>Confident with a pleasant disposition and well groomed</li>\n  <li>Ability to work under pressure and on rotating shifts</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of Opera and Microsoft Office is an advantage</li>\n</ul>",
